--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
scapeMCMC 0.9-0 (2005-09-29)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o Added functions importMCMC(), importProj(), plotAuto(), plotCumu(),
  plotDens(), plotQuant(), plotSplom(), and plotTrace().

o Added example objects xmcmc and xproj.

o Added example files mcmclike.out, params.pst, procatch.out, projspbm.out,
  recruits.pst, spawbiom.pst, and strategy.out.
